      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive! She's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making her perfect for someone who wants a reliable ride without the 'brand new' price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and she\u2019s ready for many more adventures. I\u2019ve taken great care of her, and I'm sure you'll love her just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
