      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic. At the heart of this machine is the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. This example features a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventive measure\u2014along with a recently overhauled VANOS system to ensure optimal valve timing. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics thanks to refreshed bushings and a dual-pivot front suspension setup. Power is efficiently managed by the variable M Differential Lock, providing exceptional traction through the corners. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its enthusiast-driven history, the drivetrain remains robust, with valve clearances recently adjusted to factory tolerances. This is a driver-focused vehicle with the mechanical integrity to match its performance pedigree.",
      "price": 34500.0,
