    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor, expected imperfections from careful road use. All body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are in excellent shape. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows very little wear, and the bolsters remain firm and supportive. Every electronic feature, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil service and brake inspection just completed. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. With a complete set of records and two sets of keys, this car is truly turn-key and ready for its next owner to enjoy for many miles to come.",
